    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="poem" subtype="topographical">
                <head type="title"><handShift new="#HANDJR1833-34" script="cursive" medium="ink"/>Lille</head>
                <lg rhyme="aa" met="-+|-+|-+|-+/">
                        <l>Oh red the blushing east awoke</l>
                        <l>And bright the morn on <placeName corresp="#CASSEL">Cassel</placeName>broke</l>
                        <l>Along the green hillside we flew<add rend="line_number-JR">65</add></l>
                        <l>Flashed the clear sunshine in the dew</l>
                        <l>That on the clustering herbage hung</l>
                        <l>That to the tangled corpsewood clung</l>
                        <l>That shot like stars through every shade</l>
                        <l>And glanced on every <subst><del rend="strikethrough">noontide</del><add place="above"><space quantity="20" unit="chars"/>wildwood</add></subst><add rend="line_number-JR">70</add></l>
                        <l>At length by many a wind descending</l>
                        <l>That ever to the plain were bending</l>
                        <l>Farther and farther still we pressed</l>
                        <l>From <placeName corresp="#CASSEL">Cassels</placeName> insulated crest</l>
                        <l>That back retiring further still<add rend="line_number-JR">75</add></l>
                        <l>Showed the rich outlines of its hill</l>
                        <l>And faded in the purple haze</l>
                        <l>That spoke the coming noontide blaze</l>
                        <l>That noontide blaze delayed not long</l>
                        <l>On <placeName corresp="#TOURNAI">Tournays</placeName>towers twas fierce and strong<add rend="line_number-JR">80</add></l>
                        <l>And ere we gained the middle way</l>
                        <l>The glow was like an <del rend="strikethrough">A</del> Afric day</l>
                        <l>Full upon <placeName corresp="#LILLE">Lilles</placeName> high ramparts round</l>
                        <l>On massive wall and moated mound</l>
                        <l>Shot the fierce sun his glaring ray<add rend="line_number-JR">85</add></l>
                        <l>As bent we on our burning way</l>
                        <l>Till past the narrow drawbridge length</l>
                        <l>The massive gates portcullised strength</l>
                        <l>And moat whose waves found steepy shore</l>
                        <l>Where forwrd the <subst><del rend="strikethrough">high</del><add place="below"><space quantity="14" unit="chars"/>huge</add></subst> bastion bore<add rend="line_number-JR">90</add></l>
                    <pb facs="MSIASheet24"/>
                        <l>And where the sentinels were set</l>
                        <l>High on the dizzy parapet</l>
                        <l>Till the last portals echoes woke</l>
                        <l>And <placeName corresp="#LILLE">Lille</placeName> in all it upon us sudden broke</l>
                        <l>Giving to view another scene<add rend="line_number-JR">95</add></l>
                        <l>So clear, so noble so serene</l>
                        <l>Twould seem enchantments varied hue</l>
                        <l>On palace street and avenue</l>
                        <l><add place="margin-left">&#x002A;</add>Colossal form and figure fair</l>
                        <l>Seemed moving, breathing, living there<add rend="line_number-JR">100</add></l>
                        <l>The vaulted arch where sunlight pure</l>
                        <l>Might never pierce the deep obscure</l>
                        <l>Where, broadly barred the ancient door</l>
                        <l>Was with rich carving imaged oer</l>
                        <l>Those ancient piles rose huge and high<add rend="line_number-JR">105</add></l>
                        <l>In rich irregularity</l>
                        <l>The bending gothic gable roof</l>
                        <l>Of past magnificence gave proof</l>
                        <l>The modern windows formal square</l>
                        <l>With Saxon arch was mingled there<add rend="line_number-JR">110</add></l>
                        <l>Whose stern recesses dark and deep</l>
                        <l>The figured iron stantions keep.</l>
                    </lg>
                    </div>
